text: I can't get over how funny these guys are when they're gathered for something! All the cute and amusing details, like how Yuta's nit cap keeps wandering around between different members, Ten doing the 10 % effort version of his amazing dance solo while the others laugh their butts off, Renjun proudly weight lifting two tiny screws, Jungwoo wanting to do the Black On Black ending rush with Yuta, and so on. While I'm sure the preparations for NCT Nation was a ton of work for everyone involved, I'm glad the guys were also able to smile and have fun.
